data.value:
Time passed by without you noticing it. Seems like you've enjoyed yourself playing the riddles quite a bit. It helped you calm your nerves. You feel rested.
You wander across the lower floors in search of rooms that may have anything useful inside. After a few minutes of searching, You bump into the basement door. It seemed solid and sturdy. Can't force your way this time since it needs a key.
